POST http://localhost:8021/ops/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: admin-token

{
  "productId": "P_BASIC",
  "name": "基础运营产品",
  "description": "默认配置",
  "config": "{\"maxLoan\":\"5000\"}"
}

### Update Product
PUT http://localhost:8021/ops/products/P_BASIC
Content-Type: application/json
